{"tid":1169813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[雪中送炭] 台灣晶片廠商台積電 tsmc 宣佈會維持對中國華為的手機芯片供應","createTime":"2019-05-24T15:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T15:56:06.000Z","uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"555edc4ede3640b70c3cf5fbbfc114bcdd9f1872","tid":1169813,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/05/24/台積電愛的宣言-「我們對華為不離不棄」/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80-%E3%80%8C%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%A3%84%E3%80%8D%2F&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=ba2361fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/05/24/台積電愛的宣言-「我們對華為不離不棄」/</a><br />\n<br />\n問世間情為何物，教台積電生死相許&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n台灣晶片廠商台積電 tsmc 宣佈會維持對中國華為的手機芯片供應，雙方的合作暫時不會受美國對華為的禁令所影響。不過，有分析表示美國對華為手機的禁令只有 90 日寬限期，屆時台積電是否真的可以不理歐美的反對，繼續支持華為呢 ? 似乎仍然是未知之數&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n台積電發言人 Elizabeth Sun (孫又文) 在日前舉行的全球技術論壇時表示，台積電有一套完整的出口管理系統，確保產品符合全球貿易規定，暫時不會影響華為產品的合作。據《路透社》報道指，台積電在生產過程中會使用美國技術的部份遠低於 25% ，因此不受到美國禁售令影響，所以能繼續向華為供貨。<br />\n<br />\n台積電 tsmc 是台灣最大的芯片供應商，不少國際品牌手機的處理器都是由台積電代工生產，當中包括 Apple 現正使用的 A 系列處理器，以及華為的 Kirin 處理器。受美國貿然禁令的影響，多家晶片供應商，包括 Intel、Qualcomm、XILINX 和 BROADCOM 都宣佈中止和華為的業務往來，Google 亦停止為華為新手機提供 Google 服務及 Android 系統的使用授權和支援，其後連晶片架構開發的 ARM 亦中止相關的技術授權，令華為手機無論在「軟」和「硬」開發上都受到嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣為日後中台統一作好準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217ebf675e8d06254ed1ccd24e2b4eff7677372f","tid":1169813,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為未死<br />\n<br />\n中國人又贏"},{"pid":"b42c5a91489427342934c2b4e54d66a7c57f140d","tid":1169813,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"Huawei never dies<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ac13c7004576356157d296de92a88b80cc018b","tid":1169813,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"咪睇下美國點對台積電囉，台積電有接外國生意，台灣夠疆玩野就等食屎lu"},{"pid":"058f6b8f59d96c510ac5dd7df23b08bfb21e0e57","tid":1169813,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"希望台積電唔會被美帝攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niPhone需要台積電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45905e5d648f11c0c38fe754ef216312b24e1187","tid":1169813,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"加價300% 中國有的是錢"},{"pid":"d7ec681e889f412a7840624bb071c1d3d97bb924","tid":1169813,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"058f6b8f59d96c510ac5dd7df23b08bfb21e0e57","tid":1169813,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"希望台積電唔會被美帝攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niPhone需要台積電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"哇，咁撚大鍋！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我iPhone fans <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cf11aad885a02b2156095f6cb7a136eba6df6e","tid":1169813,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ac13c7004576356157d296de92a88b80cc018b","tid":1169813,"ui